# use xinput to find mouse id. Device Accel Conststant Deceleration (YYY)
# Then set prop with <id> (YYY) VAL to change mouse sensitivity
# Alternate Option here:
# https://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/90572/how-can-i-set-mouse-sensitivity-not-just-mouse-acceleration
exec_always xinput set-prop 11 295 1.5

